### Test Denodo Express API Endpoints
### Sử dụng với VS Code REST Client extension hoặc copy vào Postman

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/health
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Lấy tất cả danh mục
GET http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Lấy danh mục theo ID
GET http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Lấy tất cả nhiệm vụ
GET http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Lấy nhiệm vụ theo ID
GET http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Lấy nhiệm vụ theo danh mục
GET http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/categories/2/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Lấy nhiệm vụ kèm thông tin danh mục
GET http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/tasks-with-categories
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Thống kê theo danh mục
GET http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/statistics/categories
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Thống kê theo độ ưu tiên
GET http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/statistics/priority
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Thống kê theo ngày
GET http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/statistics/daily
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Test với curl (copy vào terminal)
# Health check
curl -X GET "http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/health" -H "Content-Type: application/json"

# Lấy danh mục
curl -X GET "http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/categories" -H "Content-Type: application/json"

# Lấy nhiệm vụ
curl -X GET "http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/tasks" -H "Content-Type: application/json"

# Lấy thống kê
curl -X GET "http://localhost:9090/task_manager_ws/api/statistics/categories" -H "Content-Type: application/json"
